{"tid":260380,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"【拍晒手掌】張敬軒busking初體驗 亂入尖東jam歌","createTime":"2017-05-27T16:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T06:18:02.000Z","uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7df3c16d0d59ff6af6e922960e11dd7cda963fd4","tid":260380,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"【拍晒手掌】張敬軒busking初體驗 亂入尖東jam歌<br />\n<br />\n今日傍晚嚟到尖東海旁快閃加入busking team演唱，吸引途人圍觀，軒仔好causal咁先後個人solo，獻唱《音樂大童》同《青春常駐》。軒仔平日有留意街頭演出，今次係突然主動嚟jam歌，演出期間佢話係自己人生第一次busking，希望大家俾多啲掌聲支持，唱完兩首歌後更唱上癮，主動encore要唱多首《櫻花樹下》，今次就同組合互動合唱，周邊嘅人拍晒手掌，氣氛投入，軒仔覺得咁樣jam歌好有趣，亦希望大家感受到音樂大同威力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3XjsrnxoPOU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3XjsrnxoPOU&d=DSEoMFFgoShBu%2FmcIqhnAttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4a9a783f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3XjsrnxoPOU</a><br />\n段片開頭, 坐喺度嗰個女仔好似幾正 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw,   有冇人聽開 吳林峰 ,  我幾鍾意佢把聲同感染力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7665fa3df7ccc2ba1ee91ebd14e11b93736495","tid":260380,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:28:08.000Z","msg":"吳林峰 有時做 fb live ,  得十丁友睇 , 真係心酸,  但其實佢唱得好好聽 又有heart <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9697dbad671c4ce28b5854f231d8c064797f476","tid":260380,"uid":118653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"首音樂大童幾好聽，原唱係邊個? 上網搵唔到首歌，想聽下。"},{"pid":"222da42186a578e2385b940d9e7f1818d5ad72a8","tid":260380,"uid":82940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:30:25.000Z","msg":"吳林峰真係幾正"},{"pid":"0d9afe860a150cd1ec4084ac033a3fcb291a251e","tid":260380,"uid":46741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吳林峰 有時做 fb live ,  得十丁友睇 , 真係心酸,  但其實佢唱得好好聽 又有heart <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad